summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of One Hundred Seventy-three and 88/100 Dollars ($173.88) from Local Improvement District No. 1839 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing sand General Fund, for the deficiency in the fixed estimate of said district, for the improvement of West Fifty-sixth Street et al, by constructing sewer therein, under Ordinance No. 19031.
